        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued August 9 at 11:36PM MDT until August 10 at 12:00AM MDT by NWS Pueblo CO</headline>
        <description>At 1136 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Blue Lake, or
27 miles northeast of North La Junta, moving east at 25 mph.

HAZARD...Ping pong ball size hail and 60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...People and animals outdoors will be injured. Expect hail
damage to roofs, siding, windows, and vehicles. Expect wind
damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Haswell, Blue Lake, and Arlington.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
